title: 2nd floor spacious bright duplex Wedge area bus to U
map_address: 2443 Garfield Ave S near west 24th Street
posting_body: ['This lovely upper duplex is in an unusual house with a hexagonal turret in which the large comfortable bright living room is located.', 'Well maintained clean house with quiet tenants.', 'Newly painted and renovated with new bathroom and kitchen.', 'There is also a lovely study nook behind the kitchen with a skylight which can be used for a private quiet area.', 'Washer and dryer in the basement.', 'Off street parking space.', 'Wonderful location one block from the Wedge Organic Foods Coop, French Meadow Bakery, cafes, restaurants and easy buses to downtown or suburbs.', 'One block from the express bus to the U which takes 10 minutes.', 'Close to buses to downtown and light rail.', 'Institute or Arts and Walker nearby.', 'Neighborhood has a lot of artists, musicians and young professionals.', 'Rent is 1620/month; one year lease; one month rent as deposit.', 'Rent includes water and sewage, yard maintenance, snow removal.', 'It does not include other utilities, wifi, or cable.', 'Fiberoptic wifi available through city of Minneapolis on month to month contract']
